---
title: Cheddar-Crusted Chicken with Sweet Potato Mash and Snap Peas
description: Tonight's menu features cheddar-crusted chicken, sweet potato mash and roasted snap peas. The best part? Everything comes together in 30 minutes! Talk about a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-en-croute-de-cheddar-cd4843fe.jpg
